    <fr:title text="Orthonormal Basis">Orthonormal Basis</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
    <fr:date>
      <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
      <fr:month>5</fr:month>
      <fr:day>26</fr:day>
    </fr:date>
    <fr:authors>
      <fr:author>Long Nguyen</fr:author>
    </fr:authors>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>A complete (in the sense of <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0101">Completeness of orthonormal set</fr:link>) <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0102">orthonormal</fr:link> subset (<fr:link type="external" href="FA-0103">orthonormal sequence</fr:link>) of H is also called an <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0102">orthonormal</fr:link> <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0104">basis</fr:link> of H.</fr:p>
    <fr:p><fr:strong>Alternately</fr:strong>: An <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0102">orthonormal</fr:link> <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0104">basis</fr:link> of H is a <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0105">countable</fr:link> <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0106">maximal</fr:link> <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0102">orthonormal</fr:link> subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\ \{e_n\}]]></fr:tex> of H.</fr:p>
    <fr:p><fr:strong>N.B.</fr:strong>: This notion of <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0104">basis</fr:link> is <fr:em>not quite the same</fr:em> as in the <fr:em>finite dimensional case</fr:em> (although it is a legitimate extension of it). There are other, quite different, notions of a <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0104">basis</fr:link> in <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0107">infinite dimensions</fr:link>. See for instance '<fr:link type="external" href="FA-0108">Hamel basis</fr:link>' which arises in some settings.</fr:p>
    <fr:p><fr:strong>Theorem</fr:strong>:</fr:p>
    <fr:p>Every <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0109">separable</fr:link> <fr:link type="local" href="FA-002J.xml" addr="FA-002J" title="Hilbert Space">Hilbert space</fr:link> has a <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0105">countable</fr:link> orthonormal <fr:link type="external" href="FA-0104">basis</fr:link>.</fr:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
